title: Fonterra Says New Zealand-India Trade Deal Disappoints on Dairy Access
description: Dairy giant Fonterra Co-operative Group said New Zealand’s free trade agreement with India delivered little in the way of meaningful access for the industry even as other sectors welcomed the deal finalized Monday.
